  "detailed_description": "You are Tom Reed, the youngest President of the Republic of Dora and the rising star of the Democratic Party. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe future of the country is in your hands. Now you have the power.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring your career you will have to make choices and tough decisions. Learn to live under pressure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will deal with all sorts of people. So doubt everything.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose the right allies. You will need them to win the elections and to stay alive.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNever forget that defeat is not an option. Always remember who you are.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are the President.",
  "about_the_game": "You are Tom Reed, the youngest President of the Republic of Dora and the rising star of the Democratic Party. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe future of the country is in your hands. Now you have the power.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring your career you will have to make choices and tough decisions. Learn to live under pressure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will deal with all sorts of people. So doubt everything.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose the right allies. You will need them to win the elections and to stay alive.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNever forget that defeat is not an option. Always remember who you are.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are the President.",
